Customer Index: Indicates the order in which the "Customers" are processed.
Object Index: Indicates the order in which the "Objects" are processed within each "Customer".
Field Index: Indicates the order in which the "Fields" are processed within each "Object" of the "Customer".
Customer GUID: A unique code that contains the ID for the "Customer".
Object GUID: A unique code that contains IDs for both the "Customer" and the "Object"
Field GUID: A unique code that contains IDs for the "Customer", the "Object", and the "Field".
